<span id="docs-internal-guid-5ea1b61c-edbd-7e36-b356-8e9285789f72"><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">ABOUT US</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;">JOHN GOLD GROUP is a company engaged in Airline Ticketing and Cargo Forwarding Services, It’s been in the business for 21 years now and counting which has started from a single ticketing outlet known as John Gold Travel and Tours Services. It has grown in the industry through its highly quality standards of services to its customers and clients. We are now leading the airline ticketing services in Mindanao with its continuous effort to widen the scope of market here and abroad. Tying with huge companies in providing technologies in ticketing system and business model.</span></div><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt;"> Last year 2000, the company joined the cargo forwarding business known as John Gold Cargo Forwarder, to provide the fastest, most efficient and cost effective logistics solution to its clients. With opportunity seen in magnifying the services through Door to Door, John Gold has also opened the Cargo King business. </span></div></span><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Calibri"><br></font></div></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cargo King’s main objective is to prepare itself to the upcoming online shopping business in the region. As of the moment, we are appointed to be &nbsp;one of the four logistic companies to serve on a national level by a well known web based shopping site.</span></p><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></span><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 18.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 14pt;">OUR SERVICES</span></div></span><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt;">Our company is not only involved in Domestic &nbsp;AND International shipping thru air services but also offer trucking service and warehousing.</span></div></span><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 14pt;">OUR COMMITMENT</span></div></span><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt;">   * Fast and efficient on time delivery, the first in the country to be officially carried by the four leading airlines </span></div></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;* Assured drop in your cargo expenses</span></div></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;* Accurate dissemination and tracking of information rendered by our highly trained personnel.</span></div></span></s